manifestVersion: 1
id: apathecmines-hub
name: AM Hub
tagline: Unified solo mining dashboard — auto-discovers ApathecMines node apps and mines every synced coin.
icon: https://raw.githubusercontent.com/apathec/apathecmines-umbrel-store/main/apathecmines-hub/icon.png
category: bitcoin
version: "1.0.0"
port: 3080
description: |
  The ApathecMines Hub — a galaxy-themed unified dashboard for solo mining.

  Automatically detects installed ApathecMines node apps and shows their status.
  Synced nodes are ready to mine. Syncing nodes show progress with "Pending" status.
  Add new coin nodes and restart the Hub to pick them up.

  Includes Miningcore (multi-pool), Postgres, and Dozzle log viewer.

  Currently supported: BCH (more coins coming)
  Stratum: BCH on port 3333

  Connect your miner: stratum+tcp://umbrel.local:3333
developer: ApathecMines
website: https://apathecmines.com
repo: https://github.com/apathec/apathecmines-umbrel-store
support: https://github.com/apathec/apathecmines-umbrel-store/issues
gallery:
  - https://raw.githubusercontent.com/apathec/apathecmines-umbrel-store/main/apathecmines-hub/gallery-1.png
  - https://raw.githubusercontent.com/apathec/apathecmines-umbrel-store/main/apathecmines-hub/gallery-2.png
releaseNotes: >-
  Initial release. BCH solo mining with auto-discovery dashboard.
dependencies:
  - apathecmines-bch-node
path: ""
defaultUsername: ""
defaultPassword: ""
submitter: ApathecMines
submission: https://github.com/apathec/apathecmines-umbrel-store
